sequenceDiagram
    participant M as Manager
    participant FO as Field Operator
    participant S as System
    participant C as Citizen
    M->>S: Review New Citizen Report
    M->>FO: Assign Report for Resolution
    FO->>FO: Resolve Issue on Site
    FO->>S: Update Status to 'Resolved'
    S->>C: Notify Citizen of Resolution
    C->>S: View Resolution Status